pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-A-Day Ultra Cranberry 60000 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-Day Ultra Cranberry 60000 supports urinary tract and bladder health.

Thompson's One-A-Day Ultra Cranberry 60000 is a high potency cranberry formulation that can be used to/as:
- Support urinary tract & bladder health
- A source of antioxidant, reducing free radicals formed in the body & decrease their damage to body cells
- Support general health & wellbeing

Size: 60caps

Oil-Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• Helps support a healthy urinary tract.
• Helps reduce harmful bacteria adhering to the urinary tract wall.
• Provides antioxidants which help protect cells from free radical damage.
• Helps to decrease the incidence and frequency of cystitis.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional.

CAUTION

Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains:
Vaccinium macrocarpon (Cranberry) ext. 120mg
derived from fresh fruit 60g (60000mg)

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
